Foodike\", \"Startup login state resolved to onboarding\")\n39:         }\n40:     }\n41: \n42:     public override func onWindowStageCreate(windowStage: WindowStage): Unit {\n43:         Hilog.info(0x0000, \"Foodike\", \"Loading Foodike bootstrap content\")\n44:         windowStage.loadContent(\"FoodikeBootstrap\")\n45:     }\n46: }\n\n(End of file - total 46 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"package ohos_app_cangjie_entry\n\nimport kit.AbilityKit.LaunchParam\nimport kit.AbilityKit.LaunchReason\nimport kit.AbilityKit.UIAbility\nimport kit.AbilityKit.Want\nimport kit.ArkData.Preferences\nimport kit.ArkData.PreferencesValueType\nimport kit.ArkUI.WindowStage\nimport kit.PerformanceAnalysisKit.Hilog\n\nvar bootstrapStartRoute: String = \"onboarding\"\n\nclass EntryAbility <: UIAbility {\n    public init() {\n        super()\n        registerSelf()\n    }\n\n    public override func onCreate(want: Want, launchParam: LaunchParam): Unit {","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"Foodike-Harmony\\entry\\src\\main\\cangjie\\app_ability.cj","time":{"start":1782364606143,"end":1782364606152}},"id":"prt_efd358e95001eTPrHXduAgDZ7f","sessionID":"ses_102cb4ca4ffer7QLgOvHNb1oBO","messageID":"msg_efd356d71001qhm8PvtmweqGYi"}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1782364606216,"sessionID":"ses_102cb4ca4ffer7QLgOvHNb1oBO","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_W6ei1kuwqAPLaV3cC1ABkI0V","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"D:\\workspace\\Foodike\\Foodike-Harmony\\entry\\src\\main\\cangjie\\ohos_app_cangjie_entry\\app\\bootstrap_page.cj"},"output":"<path>D:\\workspace\\Foodike\\Foodike-Harmony\\entry\\src\\main\\cangjie\\ohos_app_cangjie_entry\\app\\bootstrap_page.cj</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: package ohos_app_cangjie_entry\n2: \n3: import kit.ArkUI.*\n4: import ohos.arkui.state_macro_manage.Component\n5: import ohos.arkui.state_macro_manage.Entry\n6: import ohos.arkui.state_macro_manage.State\n7: \n8: @Entry\n9: @Component\n10: class FoodikeBootstrap {\n11:     @State\n12:     var currentRoute: String = bootstrapStartRoute\n13: \n14:     @State\n15:     var isShellAtTop: Bool = true\n16: \n17:     private func navigateTo(route: String): Unit {\n18:         this.currentRoute = route\n19:         this.isShellAtTop = true\n20:     }\n21: \n22:     private func showBottomShell(route: String): Bool {\n23:         showsBottomShell(route, this.isShellAtTop)\n24:     }\n25: \n26:     private func routeTitle(route: String): String {\n27:         match (route) {\n28:             case \"onboarding\" => \"Onboarding\"\n29:             case \"login_screen\" => \"Login\"\n30:             case \"home_screen\" => \"Home\"\n31:             case \"history\" => \"History\"\n32:             case \"cart\" => \"Cart\"\n33:             case \"profile\" => \"Profile\"\n34:             case \"restaurant_details\" => \"Restaurant Detail\"\n35:             case _ => \"Unknown Route\"\n36:         }\n37:     }\n38: \n39:     private func routeSummary(route: String): String {\n40:         match (route) {\n41:             case \"onboarding\" => \"Startup lands here for logged-out users before later feature pages arrive.\"\n42:             case \"login_screen\" => \"Login remains a destination in the translated shell and is reachable from onboarding.\"\n43:             case \"home_screen\" => \"Home owns the shell chrome in the source app, including the bottom bar and cart action.\"\n44:             case \"history\" => \"History shares the shell-owned bottom bar and cart action with home.\"\n45:             case \"cart\" => \"Cart stays reachable from the shell-owned cart command and direct route selection.\"\n46:             case \"profile\" => \"Profile remains part of the route catalog even before the full feature page lands.\"\n47:             case \"restaurant_details\" => \"Restaurant detail remains a first-class route in the startup shell contract.\"\n48:             case _ => \"No summary available.\"\n49:         }\n50:     }\n51: \n52:     private func primaryActionLabel(route: String): String {\n53:         match (route) {\n54:             case \"onboarding\" => \"Continue to Login\"\n55:             case \"login_screen\" => \"Enter Home\"\n56:             case \"home_screen\" => \"Open Restaurant Detail\"\n57:             case \"history\" => \"Open Profile\"\n58:             case \"cart\" => \"Return Home\"\n59:             case \"profile\" => \"Log Out to Onboarding\"\n60:             case \"restaurant_details\" => \"Back to Home\"\n61:             case _ => \"Go Home\"\n62:         }\n63:     }\n64: \n65:     private func runPrimaryAction(route: String): Unit {\n66:         this.navigateTo(primaryActionTarget(route))\n67:     }\n68: \n69:     func build() {\n70:         Row {\n71:             Column {\n72:                 Text(\"Foodike\")\n73:                     .fontSize(42)\n74:                 Text(\"HarmonyOS startup route shell ready\")\n75:                     .fontSize(18)\n76:                 Text(\"Resolved start route: ${bootstrapStartRoute}\")\n77:                     .fontSize(16)\n78:                 Text(\"Active route: ${this.currentRoute}\")\n79:                     .fontSize(16)\n80:                     .margin(top: 8)\n81:                 Text(this.routeTitle(this.currentRoute))\n82:                     .fontSize(26)\n83:                     .margin(top: 18)\n84:                 Text(this.routeSummary(this.currentRoute))\n85:                     .fontSize(16)\n86:                     .margin(top: 8)\n87: \n88:                 Button(this.primaryActionLabel(this.currentRoute))\n89:                     .onClick({ evt =>\n90:                         this.runPrimaryAction(this.currentRoute)\n91:                     })\n92:                     .margin(top: 20)\n93: \n94:                 if (this.currentRoute == routePath(RouteId.Home) || this.currentRoute == routePath(RouteId.History)) {\n95:                     Button(if (this.isShellAtTop) { \"Simulate Scrolled Content\" } else { \"Return To Top\" })\n96:                         .onClick({ evt =>\n97:                             this.isShellAtTop = !this.isShellAtTop\n98:                         })\n99:                         .margin(top: 12)\n100:                     Text(if (this.isShellAtTop) { \"Shell chrome is visible because the shared top-level list is at the first item.\" } else { \"Shell chrome is hidden because the shared top-level list has moved away from the first item.\" })\n101:                         .fontSize(14)\n102:                         .margin(top: 8)\n103:                 }\n104: \n105:                 Text(\"Route picker\")\n106:                     .fontSize(18)\n107:                     .margin(top: 24)\n108: \n109:                 Row {\n110:                     Button(\"Onboarding\")\n111:                         .onClick({ evt => this.navigateTo(routePath(RouteId.Onboarding)) })\n112:                     Button(\"Login\")\n113:                         .onClick({ evt => this.navigateTo(routePath(RouteId.Login)) })\n114:                         .margin(left: 12)\n115:                     Button(\"Home\")\n116:                         .onClick({ evt => this.navigateTo(routePath(RouteId.Home)) })\n117:                         .margin(left: 12)\n118:                 }.margin(top: 12)\n119: \n120:                 Row {\n121:                     Button(\"History\")\n122:                         .onClick({ evt => this.navigateTo(routePath(RouteId.History)) })\n123:                     Button(\"Cart\")\n124:                         .onClick({ evt => this.navigateTo(routePath(RouteId.Cart)) })\n125:                         .margin(left: 12)\n126:                     Button(\"Profile\")\n127:                         .onClick({ evt => this.navigateTo(routePath(RouteId.Profile)) })\n128:                         .margin(left: 12)\n129:                 }.margin(top: 12)\n130: \n131:                 Button(\"Restaurant Detail\")\n132:                     .onClick({ evt => this.navigateTo(routePath(RouteId.RestaurantDetails)) })\n133:                     .margin(top: 12)\n134: \n135:                 if (this.showBottomShell(this.currentRoute)) {\n136:                     Text(\"Bottom shell commands\")\n137:                         .fontSize(18)\n138:                         .margin(top: 28)\n139:                     Row {\n140:                         Button(\"Home Tab\")\n141:                             .onClick({ evt => this.navigateTo(routePath(RouteId.Home)) })\n142:                         Button(\"Cart\")\n143:                             .onClick({ evt => this.navigateTo(routePath(RouteId.Cart)) })\n144:                             .margin(left: 12)\n145:                         Button(\"History Tab\")\n146:                             .onClick({ evt => this.navigateTo(routePath(RouteId.History)) })\n147:                             .margin(left: 12)\n148:                     }.margin(top: 12)\n149:                     Text(\"The shell-owned bottom bar and cart action appear only on home and history routes while the shared top-level list remains at the first item, matching the source route contract for this phase.\")\n150:                         .fontSize(14)\n151:                         .margin(top: 8)\n152:                 }\n153:             }.width(100.percent)\n154:         }.height(100.percent)\n155:     }\n156: }\n\n(End of file - total 156 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"package ohos_app_cangjie_entry\n\nimport kit.ArkUI.*\nimport ohos.arkui.state_macro_manage.Component\nimport ohos.arkui.state_macro_manage.Entry\nimport ohos.arkui.state_macro_manage.State\n\n@Entry\n@Component\nclass FoodikeBootstrap {\n    @State\n    var currentRoute: String = bootstrapStartRoute\n\n    @State\n    var isShellAtTop: Bool = true\n\n    private func navigateTo(route: String): Unit {\n        this.currentRoute = route\n        this.isShellAtTop = true\n    }","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"Foodike-Harmony\\entry\\src\\main\\cangjie\\ohos_app_cangjie_entry\\app\\bootstrap_page.cj","time":{"start":1782364606203,"end":1782364606215}},"id":"prt_efd358ec2001JpaPfMyvzrPzqF","sessionID":"ses_102cb4ca4ffer7QLgOvHNb1oBO","messageID":"msg_efd356d71001qhm8PvtmweqGYi"}}
