{"type":"text","timestamp":1782364606582,"sessionID":"ses_102cb4ca4ffer7QLgOvHNb1oBO","part":{"id":"prt_efd358505001Zz3IXYvQhCySGK","messageID":"msg_efd356d71001qhm8PvtmweqGYi","sessionID":"ses_102cb4ca4ffer7QLgOvHNb1oBO","type":"text","text":"The source repository’s `Flow<Boolean>` is only consumed with `first()` during splash init, so this may be an evidence mismatch rather than a missing runtime behavior. I’m checking the target startup handoff to confirm the same one-shot contract is what actually runs.","time":{"start":1782364603653,"end":1782364606580}}}
