{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1782364887487,"sessionID":"ses_102cb4ca4ffer7QLgOvHNb1oBO","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_BkglE74shfJqF6xaLgw5WkLn","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"D:\\workspace\\Foodike\\.agents\\skills\\cangjie-lang-features\\package\\README.md","offset":1,"limit":220},"output":"<path>D:\\workspace\\Foodike\\.agents\\skills\\cangjie-lang-features\\package\\README.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # 仓颉语言包管理\n2: \n3: ## 1. 包概述\n4: \n5: ### 1.1 基本概念\n6: - **包**是最小编译单元，产生 AST/静态/动态库文件\n7: - 每个包有自己的命名空间（顶层名称不允许重复，函数重载除外）\n8: - **模块**是包的集合，是最小分发单元\n9: - 模块的 `main` 入口须在其根目录中\n10: \n11: ---\n12: \n13: ## 2. 包声明\n14: \n15: ### 2.1 语法\n16: - 使用 `package pkg1.sub1` 声明，须与相对于 `src/` 的目录路径匹配\n17: - 须为文件中第一个非空/非注释行\n18: - 同一包中所有文件须有相同的包声明\n19: - 目录名须与包名匹配\n20: - `src/` 根目录的文件如果没有包声明，则默认为 `default` 包\n21: - 子包不能与顶层声明同名\n22: - Windows 上包名仅限 ASCII\n23: \n24: ### 2.2 目录结构与包声明示例\n25: ```text\n26: src\n27: |-- network\n28: |   |-- http\n29: |   |    |-- client.cj   // package default.network.http\n30: |   |    |-- server.cj   // package default.network.http\n31: |   |-- util.cj          // package default.network\n32: |-- main.cj              // 可省略包声明，默认为 default 包\n33: ```\n34: ```cangjie\n35: // client.cj — 包声明须匹配相对于 src/ 的路径\n36: package default.network.http\n37: \n38: public class HttpClient { /* ... */ }\n39: ```\n40: \n41: ### 2.3 子包与顶层声明不能同名\n42: ```cangjie\n43: // 错误示例\n44: package a\n45: public class B {}  // ❌ 错误：B 与子包 a.B 冲突\n46: ```\n47: \n48: ---\n49: \n50: ## 3. 程序入口\n51: \n52: ### 3.1 `main` 函数\n53: - `main` 是入口点，每个根包最多一个\n54: - 不能有访问修饰符\n55: - 被导入包时不会被导入\n56: - 参数：无参或 `Array<String>`\n57: - 返回类型：`Unit` 或整数类型\n58: - 定义时不使用 `func` 关键字\n59: \n60: ### 3.2 `main` 函数示例\n61: ```cangjie\n62: // 无参 main，返回整数\n63: main(): Int64 {\n64:     return 0\n65: }\n66: ```\n67: ```cangjie\n68: // 带命令行参数的 main\n69: main(args: Array<String>): Unit {\n70:     for (arg in args) {\n71:         println(arg)\n72:     }\n73: }\n74: ```\n75: ```cangjie\n76: // ❌ 错误：返回类型不能是 String\n77: main(): String { return \"\" }\n78: ```\n79: ```cangjie\n80: // ❌ 错误：参数类型只能是 Array<String>\n81: main(args: Array<Int8>): Int64 { return 0 }\n82: ```\n83: \n84: ---\n85: \n86: ## 4. 包导入\n87: \n88: ### 4.1 语法\n89: ```cangjie\n90: import fullPkg.item           // 导入单个声明\n91: import fullPkg.{a, b}         // 导入多个声明\n92: import fullPkg.*              // 导入所有可见声明\n93: import {pkg1.*, pkg2.*}       // 同时导入多个包\n94: ```\n95: \n96: ### 4.2 规则\n97: - 须在 `package` 之后、其他声明之前\n98: - 导入成员的作用域优先级低于当前包\n99: - 不允许循环依赖\n100: - 不能导入当前包\n101: - 不能导入不可见的声明\n102: \n103: ### 4.3 遮蔽与重载\n104: - 导入的名称被同名本地声明遮蔽（除非构成函数重载，此时适用重载解析）\n105: ```cangjie\n106: // package pkga\n107: package pkga\n108: public struct R {}\n109: public func f(a: Int32) {}\n110: public func f(a: Bool) {}\n111: ```\n112: ```cangjie\n113: // package pkgb\n114: package pkgb\n115: import pkga.*\n116: \n117: struct R {}                 // 本地 R 遮蔽导入的 R\n118: func f(a: Int32) {}         // 本地 f(Int32) 遮蔽导入的同签名函数\n119: \n120: func bar() {\n121:     R()     // 使用本地 R\n122:     f(1)    // 调用本地 f(Int32)\n123:     f(true) // 调用导入的 f(Bool)，构成重载\n124: }\n125: ```\n126: \n127: ### 4.4 隐式 core 导入\n128: - `String`、`Range` 等可用是因为 `core` 包被自动导入\n129: \n130: ### 4.5 import as（重命名导入）\n131: - 重命名导入以解决冲突：`import pkg.name as newName`、`import pkg as alias`\n132: - 重命名后原名不可用\n133: - 不重命名时，冲突名称在使用处报错（非导入处）\n134: - 也可 `import fullPkg` 用作命名空间限定符\n135: ```cangjie\n136: // 用 import as 解决名称冲突\n137: import p1.C as C1\n138: import p2.C as C2\n139: \n140: main() {\n141:     let _ = C1()  // 使用 p1 的 C\n142:     let _ = C2()  // 使用 p2 的 C\n143: }\n144: ```\n145: ```cangjie\n146: // 用包名作为命名空间限定符\n147: import p1\n148: import p2\n149: \n150: main() {\n151:     let _ = p1.C()  // 通过包名限定\n152:     let _ = p2.C()  // 通过包名限定\n153: }\n154: ```\n155: \n156: ### 4.6 重新导出\n157: - `public import`、`protected import`、`internal import` 重新导出导入的成员\n158: - `private import`（默认）将导入限制为文件内可见\n159: - 包本身不能被重新导出\n160: ```cangjie\n161: // package a — 重新导出子包的声明\n162: package a\n163: public import a.b.f   // 将 a.b 中的 f 重新导出\n164: \n165: public let x = 0\n166: ```\n167: ```cangjie\n168: // package a.b\n169: internal package a.b\n170: public func f(): Int64 { 0 }\n171: ```\n172: ```cangjie\n173: // 外部包可直接通过 package a 访问 f\n174: import a.f  // OK\n175: let _ = f() // OK\n176: ```\n177: ```cangjie\n178: // ❌ 错误：包不能被重新导出\n179: public import a.b  // Error\n180: ```\n181: \n182: ---\n183: \n184: ## 5. 顶层访问修饰符\n185: \n186: ### 5.1 四个级别\n187: | 修饰符 | 当前文件 | 包及子包 | 当前模块 | 全局 |\n188: |--------|---------|---------|---------|------|\n189: | `private` | ✓ | ✗ | ✗ | ✗ |\n190: | `internal`（默认） | ✓ | ✓ | ✗ | ✗ |\n191: | `protected` | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✗ |\n192: | `public` | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ |\n193: \n194: ### 5.2 默认修饰符\n195: - `package` 声明默认为 `public`\n196: - `import` 默认为 `private`\n197: - 其他顶层声明默认为 `internal`\n198: \n199: ### 5.3 访问级别约束\n200: - 声明的访问级别不能超过其使用的类型（参数、返回类型、泛型、where 约束）的访问级别\n201: - 但 `public` 声明可在内部（函数体、初始化表达式中）使用非 public 类型\n202: - 内置类型如 `Int64` 为 `public`\n203: - 同包中同名的 `private` 声明在导出时可能导致错误\n204: ```cangjie\n205: package a\n206: \n207: private func f1() { 1 }   // 仅当前文件可见\n208: func f2() { 2 }           // internal：当前包及子包可见\n209: protected func f3() { 3 } // 当前模块可见\n210: public func f4() { 4 }    // 全局可见\n211: ```\n212: ```cangjie\n213: // ❌ 错误：public 声明不能使用 internal 类型作为参数/返回值\n214: class C {}  // 默认 internal\n215: public func f1(a: C): Int64 { 0 }  // Error\n216: public let v1: C = C()      // Error\n217: ```\n\n(End of file - total 217 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# 仓颉语言包管理\n\n## 1. 包概述\n\n### 1.1 基本概念\n- **包**是最小编译单元，产生 AST/静态/动态库文件\n- 每个包有自己的命名空间（顶层名称不允许重复，函数重载除外）\n- **模块**是包的集合，是最小分发单元\n- 模块的 `main` 入口须在其根目录中\n\n---\n\n## 2. 包声明\n\n### 2.1 语法\n- 使用 `package pkg1.sub1` 声明，须与相对于 `src/` 的目录路径匹配\n- 须为文件中第一个非空/非注释行\n- 同一包中所有文件须有相同的包声明\n- 目录名须与包名匹配\n- `src/` 根目录的文件如果没有包声明，则默认为 `default` 包","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":".agents\\skills\\cangjie-lang-features\\package\\README.md","time":{"start":1782364887475,"end":1782364887486}},"id":"prt_efd39d979001XN1xUIXQUdOYSc","sessionID":"ses_102cb4ca4ffer7QLgOvHNb1oBO","messageID":"msg_efd39c939001QW3N3EXpkUYP7q"}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1782364887550,"sessionID":"ses_102cb4ca4ffer7QLgOvHNb1oBO","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_J6Q7cSGLZnhgZHW0oe3kIt1n","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"D:\\workspace\\Foodike\\.agents\\skills\\cangjie-lang-features\\project_management\\README.md","offset":1,"limit":220},"output":"<path>D:\\workspace\\Foodike\\.agents\\skills\\cangjie-lang-features\\project_management\\README.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # 仓颉语言项目管理\n2: \n3: ## 1. cjpm 概述\n4: \n5: cjpm（Cangjie Project Manager）是仓颉语言官方项目管理工具，负责模块初始化、依赖检查/更新、增量/并行编译、自定义构建命令等。\n6: \n7: ---\n8: \n9: ## 2. 核心命令\n10: \n11: ### 2.1 `init` — 初始化项目\n12: ```bash\n13: cjpm init --name myapp --type=executable\n14: cjpm init --workspace\n15: ```\n16: - 创建 `cjpm.toml` 和 `src/` 目录；可执行类型时生成 `src/main.cj`\n17: - 选项：\n18:   - `--workspace` — 创建工作区配置\n19:   - `--name <value>` — 设置根包名（默认：父目录名）\n20:   - `--path <value>` — 模块路径（默认：当前目录）\n21:   - `--type=<executable|static|dynamic>` — 输出类型（默认：`executable`）\n22: \n23: ### 2.2 `build` — 构建项目\n24: ```bash\n25: cjpm build\n26: cjpm build -V -g          # 调试模式，详细输出\n27: cjpm build -j 4            # 4 并行任务\n28: cjpm build --target <triple>  # 交叉编译\n29: ```\n30: - 先检查依赖，再调用 `cjc` 编译\n31: - 主要选项：\n32:   - `-i`/`--incremental` — 包级增量编译\n33:   - `-j`/`--jobs <N>` — 最大并行任务数\n34:   - `-V`/`--verbose` — 显示编译日志\n35:   - `-g` — 调试构建（输出到 `target/debug/bin`）\n36:   - `--coverage` — 生成覆盖率信息\n37:   - `-o`/`--output <value>` — 指定可执行文件名\n38:   - `-l`/`--lint` — 运行 `cjlint` 静态分析\n39:   - `--mock` — 启用 mock 支持\n40:   - `--target <value>` — 交叉编译目标平台\n41:   - `--skip-script` — 跳过构建脚本\n42: - 中间文件 → `target/`，可执行文件 → `target/release/bin` 或 `target/debug/bin`\n43: \n44: ### 2.3 `run` — 构建并运行\n45: ```bash\n46: cjpm run\n47: cjpm run --run-args \"arg1 arg2\"\n48: cjpm run --skip-build\n49: ```\n50: - 自动先触发 `build`\n51: - 选项：`--name`（二进制名）、`--build-args`、`--run-args`、`--skip-build`\n52: \n53: ### 2.4 `test` — 运行单元测试\n54: ```bash\n55: cjpm test\n56: cjpm test src src/koo      # 测试指定包\n57: cjpm test --filter \"MyTest*.*\"\n58: ```\n59: - 编译并运行测试用例；输出到 `target/release/unittest_bin`\n60: - 测试文件：`xxx_test.cj` 与 `xxx.cj` 并列\n61: - 主要选项：\n62:   - `--filter <value>` — 过滤测试（通配符：`*`、`MyTest*.*Test`、`-*.*exclude`）\n63:   - `--include-tags`/`--exclude-tags` — 按标签过滤\n64:   - `--timeout-each <value>` — 单个测试超时（如 `10s`、`500millis`）\n65:   - `--parallel <value>` — 并行执行\n66:   - `--no-run` — 仅编译\n67:   - `--skip-build` — 仅运行\n68:   - `--dry-run` — 打印测试列表\n69:   - `--report-path`/`--report-format` — 测试报告\n70: \n71: ### 2.5 `bench` — 运行基准测试\n72: ```bash\n73: cjpm bench\n74: cjpm bench --report-format csv\n75: ```\n76: - 运行 `@Bench` 标注的性能测试\n77: - 选项与 `test` 类似，额外支持 `--baseline-path`（对比基准）\n78: \n79: ### 2.6 `clean` — 清理构建产物\n80: ```bash\n81: cjpm clean\n82: cjpm clean --coverage\n83: ```\n84: - 移除 `target/` 目录。`--coverage` 同时清理覆盖率文件\n85: \n86: ### 2.7 `check` — 检查依赖\n87: - 打印有效的包编译顺序，或报告循环/缺失依赖\n88: \n89: ### 2.8 `update` — 更新 cjpm.lock\n90: - 同步 `cjpm.toml` 到 `cjpm.lock`；记录 git 依赖版本元数据\n91: \n92: ### 2.9 `tree` — 可视化依赖树\n93: ```bash\n94: cjpm tree -V --depth 3\n95: ```\n96: \n97: ### 2.10 `install` / `uninstall` — 安装/卸载\n98: ```bash\n99: cjpm install --path .\n100: cjpm install --git \"https://...\" --tag v1.0.0\n101: cjpm uninstall myapp\n102: ```\n103: - 支持本地和 git 两种安装模式\n104: \n105: ---\n106: \n107: ## 3. cjpm.toml 配置\n108: \n109: ### 3.1 `[package]` — 单模块配置\n110: ```toml\n111: [package]\n112: cjc-version = \"0.55.3\"       # 最低 cjc 版本（必填）\n113: name = \"myapp\"                # 模块名和根包名（必填）\n114: version = \"1.0.0\"             # 模块版本（必填）\n115: output-type = \"executable\"    # 输出类型：executable|static|dynamic（必填）\n116: description = \"My app\"        # 描述（可选）\n117: compile-option = \"-O2\"        # 额外编译选项（可选）\n118: link-option = \"\"              # 链接器选项（可选）\n119: src-dir = \"src\"               # 源码目录（默认 src）\n120: target-dir = \"target\"         # 输出目录（默认 target）\n121: ```\n122: \n123: ### 3.2 `[workspace]` — 工作区配置（与 `[package]` 互斥）\n124: ```toml\n125: [workspace]\n126: members = [\"module_a\", \"module_b\"]\n127: build-members = [\"module_a\"]\n128: test-members = [\"module_a\"]\n129: compile-option = \"\"\n130: target-dir = \"target\"\n131: ```\n132: \n133: ### 3.3 `[dependencies]` — 依赖配置\n134: ```toml\n135: [dependencies]\n136: # 本地依赖\n137: pro0 = { path = \"./pro0\" }\n138: # Git 依赖（优先级：commitId > branch > tag）\n139: pro1 = { git = \"https://...\", tag = \"v1.0.0\" }\n140: pro2 = { git = \"https://...\", branch = \"dev\" }\n141: pro3 = { git = \"https://...\", commitId = \"abc123\" }\n142: # 覆盖依赖输出类型\n143: pro4 = { path = \"./pro4\", output-type = \"dynamic\" }\n144: ```\n145: \n146: ### 3.4 `[test-dependencies]` — 测试专用依赖\n147: - 格式同 `[dependencies]`，仅在 `xxx_test.cj` 文件中可用\n148: \n149: ### 3.5 `[script-dependencies]` — 构建脚本依赖\n150: - 格式同 `[dependencies]`，仅用于 `build.cj` 脚本\n151: \n152: ### 3.6 `[replace]` — 依赖替换\n153: - 替换间接（传递）依赖：`pro0 = { path = \"./local_pro0\" }`\n154: - 仅入口模块的 `replace` 生效\n155: \n156: ### 3.7 `[ffi.c]` — C 库 FFI 依赖\n157: ```toml\n158: [ffi.c]\n159: hello = { path = \"./src/\" }\n160: ```\n161: - 开发者须预编译 `.so`/`.a` 文件到指定路径\n162: \n163: ### 3.8 `[profile]` — 配置\n164: \n165: #### profile.build\n166: ```toml\n167: [profile.build]\n168: lto = \"full\"                  # 链接时优化：full|thin\n169: incremental = true            # 增量编译\n170: ```\n171: \n172: #### profile.test\n173: ```toml\n174: [profile.test]\n175: filter = \"MyTest*\"\n176: timeout-each = \"10s\"\n177: parallel = \"4\"\n178: \n179: [profile.test.build]\n180: compile-option = \"\"\n181: mock = \"on\"                   # on|off|runtime-error\n182: \n183: [profile.test.env]\n184: MY_VAR = { value = \"abc\", splice-type = \"replace\" }\n185: ```\n186: \n187: #### profile.bench\n188: ```toml\n189: [profile.bench]\n190: report-path = \"bench_report\"\n191: report-format = \"csv\"\n192: baseline-path = \"old_report\"\n193: ```\n194: \n195: #### profile.customized-option — 自定义选项\n196: ```toml\n197: [profile.customized-option]\n198: feature_x = \"--cfg=\\\"feature=x\\\"\"\n199: optimize = \"-O2\"\n200: ```\n201: 启用：`cjpm build --feature_x --optimize`\n202: \n203: ### 3.9 `[target]` — 平台/后端特定配置\n204: ```toml\n205: [target.x86_64-unknown-linux-gnu]\n206: compile-option = \"\"\n207: link-option = \"\"\n208: \n209: [target.x86_64-unknown-linux-gnu.dependencies]\n210: pro0 = { path = \"./pro0_linux\" }\n211: \n212: [target.x86_64-unknown-linux-gnu.bin-dependencies]\n213: path-option = [\"./libs/\"]\n214: ```\n215: \n216: #### bin-dependencies — 二进制库依赖\n217: ```toml\n218: [target.name.bin-dependencies]\n219: path-option = [\"./path1\", \"./path2\"]   # 自动导入路径下的仓颉库\n220: [target.name.bin-dependencies.package-option]\n\n(Showing lines 1-220 of 319. Use offset=221 to continue.)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# 仓颉语言项目管理\n\n## 1. cjpm 概述\n\ncjpm（Cangjie Project Manager）是仓颉语言官方项目管理工具，负责模块初始化、依赖检查/更新、增量/并行编译、自定义构建命令等。\n\n---\n\n## 2. 核心命令\n\n### 2.1 `init` — 初始化项目\n```bash\ncjpm init --name myapp --type=executable\ncjpm init --workspace\n```\n- 创建 `cjpm.toml` 和 `src/` 目录；可执行类型时生成 `src/main.cj`\n- 选项：\n  - `--workspace` — 创建工作区配置\n  - `--name <value>` — 设置根包名（默认：父目录名）\n  - `--path <value>` — 模块路径（默认：当前目录）","truncated":true,"loaded":[]},"title":".agents\\skills\\cangjie-lang-features\\project_management\\README.md","time":{"start":1782364887540,"end":1782364887549}},"id":"prt_efd39d9b4001BYMj2zNoRG7sfO","sessionID":"ses_102cb4ca4ffer7QLgOvHNb1oBO","messageID":"msg_efd39c939001QW3N3EXpkUYP7q"}}
