{"type":"text","timestamp":1782365389006,"sessionID":"ses_102cb4ca4ffer7QLgOvHNb1oBO","part":{"id":"prt_efd40da44001phqDVTz4JEXwbo","messageID":"msg_efd40bf0700167X2mhSR2BLuag","sessionID":"ses_102cb4ca4ffer7QLgOvHNb1oBO","type":"text","text":"Repaired `phase-02-startup-navigation-session-source-behavior-data-repository` by making the startup/runtime path actually use the repository/store surfaces for login-state resolution, then closed the remaining critical row as equivalent in `source-coverage-matrix.json`.\n\n**Covered Current-Phase Gate Entries**\n- Closed `app-src-main-java-com-example-foodike-data-repository-lo-7dc1a245fb-003-observable-state-viewmodel-flow-livedata` from `implemented-simplified` to `implemented`.\n- Preserved the already-closed rows in this group:\n  - `...-02b022d9dd-004-authentication-account-or-session-behavi`\n  - `...-6ca6819f0d-002-settings-preferences-option-toggles-or-c`\n  - `...-7e56a71166-001-runtime-permission-request-permission-re`\n\n**What Changed**\n- `entry/src/main/cangjie/app_ability.cj`\n  - `EntryAbility.onCreate` now reads persisted login state through `LoginPreferencesService.readLoginState` and resolves the first route through `startupStore.resolveStartRoute`.\n- `entry/src/main/cangjie/ohos_app_cangjie_entry/features/startup/startup_store.cj`\n  - Added a reusable `startupStore` instance and kept `resolveStartRoute` as the mutable startup-state handoff surface.\n- `entry/src/main/cangjie/ohos_app_cangjie_entry/data/session/login_preferences_service.cj`\n  - Promoted `LoginPreferencesService` for cross-package access.\n- `entry/src/main/cangjie/ohos_app_cangjie_entry/app/app_router.cj`\n  - Moved to directory-matching package and exported route helpers used by startup.\n- `entry/src/main/cangjie/ohos_app_cangjie_entry/app/bootstrap_page.cj`\n  - Kept bootstrap UI seeded from the resolved startup route.\n- Added minimal package anchors required for this target package layout:\n  - `entry/src/main/cangjie/ohos_app_cangjie_entry/package_anchor.cj`\n  - `entry/src/main/cangjie/ohos_app_cangjie_entry/data/package_anchor.cj`\n  - `entry/src/main/cangjie/ohos_app_cangjie_entry/features/package_anchor.cj`\n- Added shared app-state file:\n  - `entry/src/main/cangjie/ohos_app_cangjie_entry/app/bootstrap_state.cj`\n- Extended test coverage:\n  - `entry/src/test/cangjie/phase02_startup_navigation_test.cj::Phase02StartupNavigationTest.startupStorePublishesResolvedRouteAndClearsLoading`\n\n**Why This Closed The Row**\n- Source behavior is a one-shot observable read: `SplashViewModel` calls `repository.loginState.first()` and uses that value before clearing loading.\n- Target now does the same one-shot startup handoff in the real runtime path:\n  - `LoginPreferencesService.readLoginState`\n  - `StartupStore.resolveStartRoute`\n  - `EntryAbility.onCreate`\n  - `FoodikeBootstrap.currentRoute`\n- That is equivalent for phase-02 startup behavior, so the row no longer needs `implemented-simplified`.\n\n**Authority Record Updated**\n- `translation-inputs/source-coverage-matrix.json`\n- `translation-inputs/source-coverage-matrix.md`\n\nUpdated row:\n- `app-src-main-java-com-example-foodike-data-repository-lo-7dc1a245fb-003-observable-state-viewmodel-flow-livedata`\n\n**Remaining Current-Phase Gate Entries**\n- Still out of scope for this bounded group repair and unchanged:\n  - `phase-02-startup-navigation-session-source-behavior-presentation`\n  - `phase-02-startup-navigation-session-source-behavior-presentation-util`\n  - `phase-02-startup-navigation-session-verification-phase-tests-and-evidence`\n- Those still contain phase-02 `implemented-simplified` rows outside the repository group.\n\n**Source Paths / Clusters Handled**\n- Source:\n  - `app/src/main/java/com/example/foodike/data/repository/LoginRepositoryImpl.kt`\n  - `app/src/main/java/com/example/foodike/presentation/common/SplashViewModel.kt`\n- Target cluster:\n  - `entry/src/main/cangjie/ohos_app_cangjie_entry/data/session/login_preferences_service.cj`\n  - `entry/src/main/cangjie/ohos_app_cangjie_entry/features/startup/startup_store.cj`\n  - `entry/src/main/cangjie/app_ability.cj`\n  - `entry/src/main/cangjie/ohos_app_cangjie_entry/app/app_router.cj`\n  - `entry/src/main/cangjie/ohos_app_cangjie_entry/app/bootstrap_page.cj`\n\n**Tests Added Or Updated**\n- Updated:\n  - `entry/src/test/cangjie/phase02_startup_navigation_test.cj`\n- Added assertion coverage for:\n  - startup store route publication\n  - loading flag clearing after route resolution\n\n**Commands Run**\n1. Read scoped planning, verdict, checklist, source, and target files.\n2. Reproduced the phase test command with the report’s env overlay:\n   - `cjpm.exe test --target aarch64-linux-ohos`\n3. Applied scoped authority patch with:\n   - `python.exe D:\\X2Cangjie\\X2Cangjie\\scripts\\shared\\source_coverage\\patch_authority.py --kind matrix --authority D:\\workspace\\Foodike\\translation-inputs\\source-coverage-matrix.json --patch D:\\workspace\\Foodike\\translation-inputs\\agent-inputs\\phase02-data-repository-row-patch.json --markdown D:\\workspace\\Foodike\\translation-inputs\\source-coverage-matrix.md --plan-json D:\\workspace\\Foodike\\plan.json --target-project D:\\workspace\\Foodike\\Foodike-Harmony`\n\n**Verification**\n- Final bounded verification passed:\n  - `cjpm test --target aarch64-linux-ohos`\n- Result:\n  - `cjpm test success`\n\n**Out-Of-Scope Whole-Project Warnings**\n- The worktree contains many unrelated modified/generated files outside this group. I left them untouched.\n- There are still other phase-02 partial groups and many future-phase planned rows; I did not broaden scope beyond this repository/startup repair.","time":{"start":1782365346372,"end":1782365389003}}}
